{"id":7756,"date":"2018-12-29T14:41:49","date_gmt":"2018-12-29T03:41:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/?p=7756"},"modified":"2025-01-21T12:40:03","modified_gmt":"2025-01-21T01:40:03","slug":"the-5-summer-hair-essentials","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/blog\/the-5-summer-hair-essentials\/","title":{"rendered":"The 5 Summer Hair Essentials"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>We&#8217;ve been waiting for it, and FINALLY Summer is here. It&#8217;s the best season by far &#8211; letting the sun-soaked days pass us by on the beach or pool side and sipping cocktails through the warm and balmy nights. Though outdoor picnics, poolside lounging and sun tanning are amazing, salt water, chlorine, humidity and UV rays from the sun can all take a brutal toll on your much loved tresses.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\nYeah, it sucks, but luckily there are plenty of products out there to help combat frizz, protect the hair from sun, add vibrancy to your colour and give the hair the extra moisture it needs during Summer. This way, we don&#8217;t have to sacrifice our healthy manes while we enjoy the summer season.<\/p>\n<p>So&#8230;make room in your bathroom shelves because here&#8217;s our run down of the five products you need for the ultimate summer mane.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">R + Co Rockaway Salt Spray<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-6603 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-156x300.jpeg\" alt=\"R+Co\u00a0Rockaway Salt Spray\" width=\"156\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-156x300.jpeg 156w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-532x1024.jpeg 532w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-200x385.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-400x770.jpeg 400w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-600x1155.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray-500x962.jpeg 500w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/rockaway-salt-spray.jpeg 665w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 156px) 100vw, 156px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Everyone looks good at the beach. Well, at least their hair does. The sun, sand and wind add amazing amounts of volume to hair, leaving it rough and sexy. The number one go to for that un-done, beach babe look &#8211; a must have for Summer.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Oribe Surfcomber Toussled Texture Mousse<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4322\" src=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-108x300.jpg\" alt=\"Oribe Surfcomber Tousled Texture Mousse\" width=\"108\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-108x300.jpg 108w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-768x2129.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-369x1024.jpg 369w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-43x120.jpg 43w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-180x500.jpg 180w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-79x220.jpg 79w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-200x555.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-400x1109.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-600x1664.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-800x2218.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched-1200x3327.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/04\/Surfcomber-tousled-texture-mousse-retouched.jpg 1584w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 108px) 100vw, 108px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Sexy, surfed-in hair is no longer the domain of beachgoers in their tropical climes. Texturize your locks with\u00a0Oribe Surfcomber Toussled Texture Mousse, a hydrating mousse that creates perfectly imperfect separation for that effortlessly tousled look &#8211; this will be everything for those low maintenance, HOT days.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kerastase Maskeratine<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5232\" src=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-120x120.jpg 120w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-500x500.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-66x66.jpg 66w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-200x200.jpg 200w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/maskeratine.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Is your hair becoming a victim to the unwanted humidity that can come from Summer? Are your days on the beach leaving it feeling dry and crispy? Kerastase Maskeratine is the perfect indulgence that deeply conditions providing maximum frizz control and extreme softness and suppleness for fine to coarse, unruly hair.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">R + Co Palm Springs Pre-Shampoo Treatment<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-6529\" src=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask-133x300.jpeg\" alt=\"r + co palm springs pre shampoo treatment mask\" width=\"133\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask-133x300.jpeg 133w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask-454x1024.jpeg 454w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask-200x451.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask-400x901.jpeg 400w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask-500x1127.jpeg 500w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/06\/palm-springs-pre-shampoo-mask.jpeg 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 133px) 100vw, 133px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you hair is worn out from heat-styling, coloring or spending countless hours working on your tan, send it on a weekly getaway to an oasis of repair with PALM SPRINGS Treatment Mask. A soothing cocktail of oils, butters and extracts deep conditions, strengthens and adds tons of shine to help hair look and feel well-rested and ready to go back to the grind.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Davines Love Curl Revitalizer<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5878\" src=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-188x300.jpeg\" alt=\"davines love curl revitaliser 250ml\" width=\"188\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-188x300.jpeg 188w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-768x1229.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-640x1024.jpeg 640w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-200x320.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-400x640.jpeg 400w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-600x960.jpeg 600w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser.jpeg 800w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-500x800.jpeg 500w, https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/02\/love-curl-revitaliser-700x1120.jpeg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 188px) 100vw, 188px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">A summer must-have for those with textured hair, Davines Love Curl Revitalizer enhances the vitality of curls between shampoos, or after a long day being in and out of the water. The ultra fine mist spray also has an anti-frizz effect, while enhancing the shine and softness in the hair. The newest addition to your summer beach bag!<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! Your mane&#8217;s summer wardrobe is sorted. Let us know what your summer favourites for your locks are.<\/p>\n<p>Love,<br \/>\nLuxe<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font: 12px\/normal 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #454545; font-family: Helvetica Neue; font-size: medium;\"><br \/>\n<!--EndFragment --><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We&#8217;ve been waiting for it, and FINALLY Summer is here. It&#8217;s the best season by far &#8211; letting the sun-soaked days pass us by on the beach or pool side and sipping cocktails through the warm and balmy nights. Though outdoor picnics, poolside lounging and sun tanning are amazing, salt water, chlorine, humidity and UV [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":7773,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[7],"tags":[33],"class_list":["post-7756","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-blog","tag-update"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7756","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7756"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7756\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12502,"href":"https:\/\/www.luxeconceptsalon.com.au\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7756\/revisions\/12502"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/ww